            <string language="en-US">Follow The Rules</string>
          </title>
          <language>en-US</language>
          <description>
            <string language="en-US">This flipchart gives students the opportunity to learn that counting up is like adding numbers, and counting back is like subtracting numbers. There are a total of 26 pages in this flipchart with different rules on each page and pages set for you to create your own rules. Various shapes are also identified. It will work great as a center also.</string>
